{"title":"兰江风情（二首）","authors":["吴晓"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":5,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰江风情（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浙江金华  吴晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰江夜歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"入夜的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兰江就开始妆扮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半城灯盏，一头珠串，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明明灭灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流水洗濯她的端庄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渡头在这时涨起了繁忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对岸是花事正闹的沙洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜游者的余兴踏飞宿鸟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黛色的波影里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"末班的渡船还在把谁等候。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更晚的是埠头的捣衣女，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻轻、轻轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深夜里仍在拍响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这温存的生活的节奏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"题兰花女塑像"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海边的凤凰树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"微曦突出了柔美的曲线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨风模糊了唇边的笑意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"独立的少女峰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"未升的月吻着纷披的秀发，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含蓄了那执着的主题。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨夜一个梦留在江边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雾纱的朦胧中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"笼住了更多的美丽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有兰花，透着岁月芬芳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风里雨里，永远明朗地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向人们传递温馨的祝福。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}